{"tid":527182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老柒柒，睇睇wiki 香港，睇到段野你地仲捨得放棄香港咩","createTime":"2018-01-12T11:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T12:45:32.000Z","uid":59014,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c78b6f5b767402cb72f2fae86a54c198df4db963","tid":527182,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"香港是全球重要的國際金融、服務業及航運中心，連續多年蟬聯全球最自由經濟體，並以優良治安、廉潔社會、簡單稅制和健全的法律制度而聞名於世因此有「東方之珠」的美譽。「亞洲國際都會」則為官方定位的香港品牌。香港同時為全球其中一個最安全、經濟最發達、生活水平最高、競爭力最高、最適宜居住及人均壽命最長的大都會。空氣污染、貧富懸殊、政制發展等則為該地主要的社會問題。<br />\n<br />\n連歐洲一d 大城市都無香港咁出名"},{"pid":"96acb26d1102691f493afd930cbec8c0d285c103","tid":527182,"uid":108421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"最適宜有錢居住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd82a99f15e1a35cccba6a0799ea6de29c9ec5c9","tid":527182,"uid":11001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"空氣污染、貧富懸殊、政制發展等則為該地主要的社會問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85e34b942b9adeaa3777a059407dae3b27feabf","tid":527182,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"so what 屌你老母窮人就烏煙瘴氣"},{"pid":"0af7bbd29233a4db3b1fca6c8bc879f8133e9336","tid":527182,"uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"而家都無曬啦<br />\n仲唔移民留係度等死咩"},{"pid":"048db8d631c1485743d265d81ee8b58a48ca6507","tid":527182,"uid":77092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7e77f9c0e72fcf710b3efb35f21f73441a96d04","tid":527182,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"